updatesearchindex extension README

What is the updatesearchindex extension?
========================================

updatesearchindex is an eZ publish patch extension
that provides a anternate replacement for the stock 
eZ publish search index update shell scripts.


updatesearchindex version
=========================

The current version of updatesearchindex is 0.0.1.
Last Updated: April 14, 2007

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-0.0.1


