Requirements
============

The following requirements exists for using updatesearchindex extension:

o  eZ publish version:

   Make sure you use eZ publish version 3.4 or higher. Recommened 3.9.2. Tested with 3.7.5, 3.8.6 and 3.9.2

o  PHP version:

   Make sure you have PHP 4.4.2 or higher. Recommended 4.4.6. Tested with 4.4.2

o  You must have access via ssh shell to your eZ publish installation.


Installation
============

Details on installing updatesearchindex located in the file doc/INSTALL.


Usage
=====

1. Install the patched files into your eZ publish installation

2. Review the available documentation on how to run the command: 
   doc/INSTALL and doc/example.cron

3. Run the command via ssh shell, cron or scheduled tasks


